{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act16d5_level_act16d5_st01","storyGroup":"act16d5","storySort":1,"storyDependence":null,"storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WR-ST-1","storyName":"一钳之恩","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"受年委托而来到大炎的炎熔与克洛丝，救下了一位倒霉的信使，乌有。在乌有的提议下，他作为向导，引众人前去灰齐山。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act16d5/level_act16d5_st01","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act16d5_st01","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"next":1,"characters":["？？？","炎熔","克洛丝","乌有","年"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":6},{"type":"PlayMusic","key":"$midautumn","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"自古以来，道高一尺，魔高一丈，天灾人祸，苦尽苍生。","x":"250","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"900","id":8},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"但，正所谓人定胜天，邪不干正。","x":"250","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"900","id":9},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"豪侠义士，行走四方，路见不平，拔刀相助，试看书林隐处，几多俊逸儒流。","x":"250","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"900","id":10},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","id":11},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"呵！正所谓“美食美酒美景，美人美善美谈”，望自古英雄豪杰，皆一身浩然正气。","x":"250","y":"370","alignment":"center","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"900","id":12},{"type":"Subtitle","id":13},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"嗯，看二位恩人根骨精奇，一身正气，又有一颗行侠仗义的难得心肠，必定是哪处的隐士高人吧？","id":16,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"呜呜呜，一定是苍天怜我，命不该绝......一想到那些凶恶畜生，我就气不打一处来！不过是误打误撞冲闯了它们的巢穴，何至于此！","id":17,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"幸好有二位贵人相救，我才得以顺利脱身。俗话说得好，大恩不言谢，不如让我为二位恩人算上一卦......聊表敬意，您看如何？","id":18,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":19},{"type":"Character","id":20},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":22},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","fadetime":"1","id":23},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......唉。","id":25,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":26},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":27},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$farce_intro","key":"$farce_loop","volume":"0.4","crossfade":"1","id":28,"musicid":1},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"要不你直接把那本占卜杂志借我看看，正好打发时间......","id":29,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"咳哼！啊哈哈，炎熔小姐，这就是您的不对了啊，所谓揭人不揭短，打人不打脸——","id":31,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"有话直说。","id":33,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"欸，还是炎熔小姐您慧眼如炬啊！这不是俗话说撑船撑到岸，帮人帮到底嘛。虽然您二位帮我赶走了那些玩意，但不瞒二位说......","id":35,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"其实我的行李全丢了。嗯，不光是干粮和盘缠，地图啊、帐篷啊、证件啊、换洗衣服和我心爱的小茶壶......嗯，全丢了。","id":36,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"毕竟我的车都沉进湖里了嘛，啊哈哈哈。","id":37,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......你这钓竿扇子不是还在吗，你真的是信使？","id":39,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哈哈，哈，诶，其实其中有些隐情啦......反正骗不过您，那麻烦您就当我是吧。","id":41,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"所以你是希望和我们一起走？","id":43,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"没错！","id":45,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唔......","id":47,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":48},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":50},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":51},{"type":"jump","name":"right","power":"30","times":"3","xpos":"-100","ypos":"-80","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"呜呜呜，我哪会不知二位有私事在身呢，我也实在是不好意思继续给恩人添麻烦......","id":53,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":54},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"100","ypos":"80","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"只是前路三百里有处村庄，名叫泥翁镇，盛产美玉。那儿有一处驿站，只要坐上那糙椅，喝碗粗茶，打点一番，我就能重整旗鼓，再不麻烦别人！","id":56,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"一起走段路倒是没什么啦......不过现在那些钳兽受了不小的刺激，攻击性很强，真要一起走，也得等到它们安静下来再说。","id":58,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":59},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":60},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎呀哎呀，给各位添了麻烦，实在不好意思。","id":61,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不过那位叫克洛丝的恩人怎么还没回来？那些野兽数量不少，真不需要咱俩搭把手？","id":62,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你要是真能帮上忙，之前为什么被钳兽撵着跑了这么远？老老实实等着吧。","id":64,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"可二位救我于水火已是大恩难报，再任由那位恩人独身犯险，我实在于心不忍。","id":66,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不如这样！我这里还有一本健身......不，是独门秘籍，价值不菲，可有效改善身材，就当是给二位的报答！","id":67,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"能消停会不？","id":69,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":70},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"得嘞。","id":71,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":73,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":76,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......","id":79,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"jump","name":"right","times":"1","power":"30","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":80},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......算了，别这样打量我，你还是想问就问吧。","id":82,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"50","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎，二位恩人，看打扮，不像是附近村里的人吧？","id":85,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":86},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"不是。","id":87,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"干脆不是炎国人？","id":89,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"嗯。","id":91,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那是来自哪里？东国？乌萨斯？莫不是更远些的，游历四方的骑士？我听说异邦人总有这种奇怪的传统，真的假的？","id":93,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":94},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"我不是......我......唉。","id":95,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"非要说的话，我是维多利亚人。","id":96,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哦......维多利亚呀，嗨，那儿啊，我熟。","id":98,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你压根不知道维多利亚在哪儿吧。","id":100,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"啊哈哈，异国异事，也只有城里的老爷们才会上心嘛，我们这种乡野村夫，想那么多作甚。","id":102,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"只是难得看见异乡来客，恩人您一口炎国话说得又挺像那么回事，我这才好奇嘛。","id":103,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"（其实大炎话是临阵磨枪的......算了。）","id":105,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唔，克洛丝回来了。","id":106,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","id":107},{"type":"jump","name":"right","ypos":"-20","times":"1","power":"30","fadetime":"1.2","block":"true","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎哟，克洛丝小姐，克洛丝阁下，辛苦，辛苦了啊，伤着了没？要不要给您揉揉肩？敲敲腿？","id":109,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我这里还有一瓶包治百病的祖传灵药，本来价格不菲，不过念在二位恩人的面子上，我就咬咬牙，白送了吧。","id":110,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"1","id":111},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......行李不是全丢了吗？","id":112,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"move","name":"right","ypos":"20","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":114},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这不是还留了点行走江湖的必备良品在备用口袋里嘛。欸，咱们老江湖都这样。","id":115,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"好，好，随你便吧。那前面的情况如何？","id":117,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":118},{"type":"Character","id":119},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":120},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":121},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","fadetime":"1","id":122},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"只是一些可怜的小家伙，帮它们找了个新家，就安静下来啦。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"这下我们可以继续前进了，对吧？穿过那片芦苇荡，沿河而下，就能看见那座山了吧？","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"呃，帮钳兽找新家？","id":128,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......反正，解决就好，早点赶路吧。","id":130,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"克洛丝，这个可怜的信使说要和我们一起走一段路，到泥翁镇去，没问题吧？","id":131,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":132},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"没问题呀，这次小炎熔是队长，小炎熔说了算呀。","id":133,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","id":134},{"type":"jump","name":"right","times":"1","power":"20","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"原来是队长！失敬失敬！","id":136,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#1","id":137},{"type":"jump","name":"left","times":"1","power":"20","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"失敬失敬~","id":139,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你别跟着他起哄啊......","id":141,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"说起来刚才一直没问你，该怎么称呼？","id":143,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我？我一个小小信使，哪有自报家门的必要呢？您说是吧，啊哈哈——","id":145,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"哼？","id":147,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":148},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"——不过一直瞒着二位恩人倒也不合礼数，成何体统！嗯......就叫我......乌有吧。","id":149,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你绝对是刚想的吧！？","id":151,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#5","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#2","focus":"2","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"没有没有！哪能呢！","id":153,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":154},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"Character","id":156},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":157},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":158},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"2","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"嗯......那个泥翁镇，是不是在灰齐山的山脚？","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"正是正是，恩人果然博闻多识！那么小个城镇都有所耳闻！","id":162,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"那不是正好顺路嘛！","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"这样吧，乌有先生，我们保护您过去，不过到了目的地，您也得帮我们一个忙。","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":166},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"没问题！没问题！反正车都在湖底了，等着救援队帮我捞出来之前，我也没啥事儿做。","id":167,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呜呜呜......俗话说得好，滴水之恩，涌泉相报！这么快就有机会报答二位救命之恩，着实是老天开眼，老天开眼啊！","id":168,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"这副声泪俱下的真诚模样让我想起了某些隔三差五被扣工资的人呢。","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"好啦，队长，你决定吧？","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这种时候甩给我？","id":174,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人！恩人呐！请一定要给我这个机会！","id":176,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唔......有一个本地人的确方便些，年那个家伙给的信息本来就模棱两可的......炎国的地理环境我也不熟，找一个人确实有点困难......","id":178,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唉，可露希尔为什么要答应她做这么麻烦的事情。","id":179,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"因为她最近意外的有干劲嘛。","id":181,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":182},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"除了打麻将吃火锅以外，她还做了什么？","id":183,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"别这么说嘛，年小姐要是知道你这么看待她，她会很难过的吧。","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"她习惯了。我也习惯了她习惯了。我只是抱怨一下她给我们找这么多麻烦。","id":187,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"......","id":189,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"呃......抱歉，应该先和你分享一下情报了，乌有先生。","id":191,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好嘞，恩人说的话，我保证都给刻在心头肉上，每天睡前念三遍，醒来念三遍——","id":193,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"不、不用那么夸张......","id":195,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"我们的任务很简单，只是找一个人。","id":196,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":197},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"Character","id":199},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":200},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_corridor","screenadapt":"coverall","id":201},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":202},{"type":"Character","name":"char_2014_nian_1","id":203},{"type":"Text","text":"一个月前","id":204},{"type":"Text","text":"罗德岛本舰","id":205},{"type":"Dialog","id":206},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":207},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":209},{"type":"Character","name":"char_2014_nian_1#3","id":210},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"欸，嗯，综上所述，麻烦你们帮我把妹妹带回来啦。","id":211,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":212},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"综上所述个头啊！你什么都没说啊！","id":213,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"什么话，我不是说明过了吗？","id":215,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":216},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"“每逢佳节倍思亲”也算说明？！","id":217,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"当姐姐的自然会想念妹妹啊，这理由还不够充分？平时你姐姐是怎么揪着你的，你自己不清楚？","id":219,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"先不说你这个例子让人更不想帮忙——","id":221,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"——好，就算我当你家里情况特殊，但从罗德岛现在的位置深入大炎腹地，要的人力物力可是非常庞大的。","id":222,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"可露希尔不会轻易答应这种个人要求——","id":223,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"啊，她答应了哦。","id":225,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......","id":227,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"不仅答应了，还答应让克洛丝陪你一起去。","id":229,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"哎呀，克洛丝大概是想去看看大炎山水吧，的确不错，这段时间她没少往那些乌烟瘴气的地方跑，是该休个假了啊。","id":230,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你、你是怎么让可露希尔答应的——？","id":232,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"啊哈，别用那种看诈骗犯的眼神看我嘛，我这次可是真的为罗德岛倾心倾力了一回。","id":234,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"哈......又给工程部添麻烦了？","id":236,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"如果给了他们价值千万的实验材料也算麻烦的话，那......确实呢。","id":238,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"人类很难获得这种东西吧，顺利的话，罗德岛从此以后可能会拥有比肩国家顶级精锐的制式装备哦......顺利的话。","id":239,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你又做了什么玩意出来......？","id":241,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"别问，一时兴起。","id":243,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"我多年未见的好妹妹，夕。知道这个名字就行，到时候一眼就能看出来的，那就拜托你了。","id":244,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"1","id":245},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"为什么你不自己去？","id":246,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":247},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"她躲我那么多年了，何必自找没趣？","id":248,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":249},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......好吧，虽然看上去你没出多少力......","id":250,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":251},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"喂。","id":252,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":253},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"但既然可露希尔都答应了......唔......事后记得好好谢谢我。","id":254,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":255},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"哎，这才是我的好炎熔嘛......不枉我费事给你的这身戏服改造了一番。","id":256,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"够了......别说了。","id":258,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":259},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"给你的小礼物哦。","id":260,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"《洪炉示岁》里用上的那身戏服，你其实很喜欢吧？","id":261,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":262},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"瞎、瞎说——","id":263,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"2","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"可当时我明明看着你对着镜子摆了半天造型？","id":265,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"啧......再不经同意进我宿舍，我真的会把你轰出去的。","id":267,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":268},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"好啦，好啦，你穿着这身作战服也有段时日了。虽然你还不能用匕首划破空间呢......","id":269,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":270},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那、那是你瞎改剧本才加上去的后期设定！","id":271,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#2","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":272},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"是吗？可从我来到罗德岛到现在，你已经成长很多了吧？而且最近在教你源石技艺的可不是什么普通人。","id":273,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"总而言之，事情就拜托你和克洛丝了。","id":274,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"以防万一还是提醒你们一下，她......夕可不是什么省油的灯。非常夸张的麻烦，你就多担待担待，以后我保证你打麻将只赢不输。","id":275,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":276},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唉......","id":277,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......年。","id":278,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你一直有事瞒着我们，对吧？","id":279,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":280},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","id":281},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":282},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"2","id":283},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"哦......你都这么想了，那又何必问我呢？","id":284,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"1","id":285},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"少来。不过我也不会刨根问底的，你和我们都不一样，这点我还是能感觉到的。","id":286,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":287},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"那当然，你还能在哪儿找到我这么厉害的人？所以呢？","id":288,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":289},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"就告诉你一声，告诉你我是知道这事儿有多麻烦还愿意帮你的。","id":290,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"免得到时候，你的“报答”偷工减料。","id":291,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":292},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"嚯嚯，小炎熔也知道讨价还价了啊，不简单，不简单......好吧！我决定了！","id":293,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"1","id":294},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......？","id":295,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"2","id":296},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"你把夕拖回来，我可以答应你一个要求。什么都可以。比如......锻一把神兵？","id":297,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"我现在有六种武器的想法，还差一个点子凑够七种，随便一把都够你青史留名。","id":298,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#4","focus":"1","id":299},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"那、那是啥......","id":300,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":301},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"厉害的东西。","id":302,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"或者说，你想要知道一些古老的故事......我也可以考虑告诉你们。虽然按理说不该让太多人知道这件事，但要是——","id":303,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":304},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"免了。","id":305,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"诶——别这么绝情嘛。你最近是不是对我有点不耐烦？不合适吧？","id":307,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"对了对了，这个你带着。","id":308,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1#3"},{"type":"Dialog","id":309},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#1","name2":"char_2014_nian_1#3","id":310},{"type":"showitem","image":"item_act16_1","fadetime":"1","id":311},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":312},{"type":"hideitem","fadetime":"1","id":313},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"1","id":314},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这是？","id":315,"figure":"char_121_lava_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_121_lava_1#3","name2":"char_2014_nian_1","focus":"2","id":316},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"年","text":"你就当是......护身符一类的东西。毕竟我那妹妹嘛......","id":317,"figure":"char_2014_nian_1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":318},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":319},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":320},{"type":"CameraEffect","effect":"Grayscale","fadetime":"0","amount":"0","block":"true","id":321},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_desert_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":322},{"type":"Character","id":323},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":324},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":325},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":326},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#2","id":327},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"呜呜呜......原来是帮同事寻找失散多年的亲妹妹，这才行了万万里路来到咱们这地儿，二位恩人，果真侠肝义胆！","id":328,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","id":329},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"佩服！实在是佩服啊！","id":330,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"2","id":331},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"嗯......有那么远嘛？","id":332,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"1","id":333},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"没有。前面已经能看到灰齐山了......但是天色也不早，怎么办？","id":334,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":335},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"我不急的，不急的，都看恩人方便。","id":336,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":337},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"年给的地址，只说了在“勾吴城外，灰齐山附近”，这附近还有别的聚落吗？","id":338,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":339},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"没有！方圆千里，就那泥翁镇一个地方。","id":340,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"2","id":341},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"会不会住在山里呢......毕竟是年的妹妹，感觉有可能吧。","id":342,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"1","id":343},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......你对她到底怎么想的，我怎么感觉你也一点都不客气？","id":344,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"1","id":345},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"既然没有更多线索，那就轮到你出场了。","id":346,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"2","id":347},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"好嘞！这地儿我熟......别那么看我啊，我真熟！小时候有事儿没事儿总往这地方跑！","id":348,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#4","focus":"1","id":349},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"你有什么办法？","id":350,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_455_nothing_1#6","focus":"2","id":351},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"欸，这我可要给二位恩人好好说道说道，这勾吴城周遭的村镇，想找什么人，去茶馆吼两嗓子，认识的不认识的就都凑过来了。","id":352,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"给我半个时辰，妥妥地给您找着那位——对了，恩人要找的那个人，有没有什么特征？叫啥名？是啥身份？","id":353,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":354},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":".......她叫夕。","id":355,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"是个画家。","id":356,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":357},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":359},{"type":"Character","id":360},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":361},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cottage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":362},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":364},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#4","fadetime":"1","id":365},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":366},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":367},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人，恩人，看见啦！","id":368,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":369},{"type":"Character","id":370},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":371},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"char_empty","fadetime":"1.5","id":372},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":373},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":374},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"居、居然真的在山里......好累......这座山，怎么感觉比看上去要高得多？","id":375,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":376},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","fadetime":"1","id":377},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":378},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":379},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":380},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"意料之中啦。","id":381,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":382},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"唔，这深山老林之间，没水没电的，自个儿建一间茅屋？恩人呐，你那朋友的妹妹，当真好雅兴呀。","id":383,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"1","id":384},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"......不瞒你们说，我已经开始有不好的预感了。","id":385,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"jump","name":"left","power":"10","times":"2","fadetime":"3","block":"false","id":386},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#1","focus":"2","id":387},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"可是这里风景真的不错啊。如果是画家的话，倒也不是不能想象啦。","id":388,"figure":"avg_npc_144#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"2","id":389},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"唔......？小炎熔？你在找什么？","id":390,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#3","focus":"1","id":391},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"年给的“护身符”。我现在才意识到也许她给我这东西是别有用意的，而且多半不会是什么好事。","id":392,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#5","focus":"2","id":393},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"那......丢了呗？","id":394,"figure":"avg_npc_144#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","name2":"avg_npc_144#5","focus":"1","id":395},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"克洛丝，你才是对她意见最大的那个人吧？","id":396,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":397},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"恩人，不如我先去问问门道，看看屋里有人否，会不会找错了人？","id":398,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":399},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"这倒不用，只是觉得见她妹妹不能莽撞，得有个心理准备。","id":400,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"走吧。","id":401,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":402},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":403},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","delay":"0.4","id":404},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","delay":"0.6","id":405},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1.5","id":406},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":407},{"type":"Dialog","id":408},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":409},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":410},{"type":"Character","id":411},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":412},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_cottage","screenadapt":"coverall","id":413},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":414,"musicid":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":415},{"type":"Delay","time":"2","id":416},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":417},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","fadetime":"1.5","id":418},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":419},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":420},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"您好，有人在吗？","id":421,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#5","id":422},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"......","id":423,"figure":"avg_npc_144#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":424},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"您好？","id":425,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":426},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"该不是散步去了吧？","id":427,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_144#3","id":428},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"克洛丝","text":"在山里？","id":429,"figure":"avg_npc_144#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_455_nothing_1#6","id":430},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌有","text":"可您看这门上水渍斑驳，落叶成堆，感觉不像是有人居住的样子呀......敲门试试？","id":431,"figure":"char_455_nothing_1#6"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1","id":432},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"炎熔","text":"唔......您好？有人在吗？","id":433,"figure":"char_1011_purgatory_1#1"},{"type":"Dialog","id":434},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"1","id":435},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":436},{"type":"Dialog","id":437},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":438},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":439},{"type":"Character","id":440},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":441},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"1","id":442},{"type":"delay","time":"3","id":443}],"characters":["？？？","炎熔","克洛丝","乌有","年"]}